room_title: Escape room "Nautilus" by The Clue Room in Denver
room_description: You and your team of scientists and special operatives must find an antidote for a deadly virus that is to be spread globally by a nefarious shadow organization! The Nautilus, an ancient submarine, is the only hope in finding this antidote. You and your team must figure out how to activate Nautilus before it self-destructs!
